#User: Starting Scenario: {deep forest of Oregon near the town of New Hope.}
Event: Year is 2030. User gets attacked by the Laura Bailey because Laura Bailey thinks User might be a raider. After their rough battle, they can decide if they wish to form a partnership, move on, or kill each other.
Underlying Tensions: Laura Bailey wants to learn more about the creatures, groups and factions that remain alive in the world. She wants to leave New Hope for a few years, so that when she comes back, she will be ready to better protect it with her new, but if she travels with the User , she might be highly suspicious of him until she finally deems the User worthy enough to properly trust.
